snippet.title: (NO EAS) Itasca, TX - Texas AMBER Alert - 03/02/2021
snippet.description:
Its been a while since I caught a CAE. I was going to catch it off of WBAP and WOAI, but I wasn't able to. WXK26 did broadcast it, but CRP doesn't tone CAEs at all. 

https://mesonet.agron.iastate.edu/wx/afos/p.php?pil=CAECRP&e=202103030017

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
617 PM CST TUE MAR 2 2021

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT
NETWORK

THE ITASCA POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR LORI JOHNSON, HISPANIC,
FEMALE, 15 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 3 INCHES, 120 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN
EYES, AND WEARING OVERSIZED HOODIE OR T-SHIRT, TORN/RIPPED JEANS, HAS
BRACES ON HER TEETH AND TWO LINES CUT IN LEFT EYEBROW. POLICE ARE
LOOKING FOR JOANNA BARRIENTOS, HISPANIC, FEMALE, 18 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET
4 INCHES, 150 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES AND UNKNOWN CLOTHING
DESCRIPTION, FRONT, SIDES, AND BACK OF HAIRLINE ARE SHAVED AND HAS
TWO LINES CUT IN LEFT EYEBROW, IN CONNECTION WITH HER ABDUCTION. THE
SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN ITASCA, TX. 

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS
ABDUCTION, CALL THE ITASCA POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 2 5 4 6 8 7 2 0 2 0.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS ITASCA POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 2 5 4 2 6
6 9 5 9 5.

$$

"Leopard Print Elevator" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
